Launch the ÃHierarchy SetupÄ function and go to the ÃTrade AttributesÄ tab.

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000597-0/img10.png"><br>

You can select the number of trade attributes you want to manage (they can also be added at a later stage after launch). 
It is possible to perform the setup on each structure by entering from the following menus.

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000597-0/img11.png"><br>

You identify which of the various data structures you want to use as trade attributes.

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000597-0/img12.png"><br>